  "text": "Found all Kafka consumer group partition assignment strategy implementations in the apache/kafka repository. The assignment strategies are located in the clients module:\n\n1. **RangeAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/RangeAssignor.java) - Implements range-based partition assignment, dividing partitions sequentially per-topic to consumers in lexicographic order. Extends AbstractPartitionAssignor and supports rack-aware assignment.\n\n2. **RoundRobinAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/RoundRobinAssignor.java) - Implements round-robin partition assignment across all subscribed topics and consumers. Extends AbstractPartitionAssignor and ensures uniform distribution when all consumers have identical subscriptions.\n\n3. **StickyAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/StickyAssignor.java) - Implements sticky assignment that minimizes partition movement across rebalances while maintaining balanced distribution. Extends AbstractStickyAssignor and uses eager rebalancing protocol.\n\n4. **CooperativeStickyAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/CooperativeStickyAssignor.java) - Cooperative version of StickyAssignor that supports cooperative rebalancing protocol. Extends AbstractStickyAssignor and only revokes partitions that must transfer ownership.\n\n5. **AbstractPartitionAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/AbstractPartitionAssignor.java) - Base class for partition assignors that implements ConsumerPartitionAssignor interface. Provides common functionality including partition counting and rack-aware assignment logic.\n\n6. **AbstractStickyAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/AbstractStickyAssignor.java) - Abstract base class for sticky assignment implementations that extends AbstractPartitionAssignor. Provides the core sticky assignment algorithm and member data serialization."
}

